{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo jums irr ja-eet pahr\nko Jardanu/ ka juhs nahkat to\nSemni eemantoht/ ko tas KUNGS\njuhtu Deews jums dohs/ un jums\nbuhs to par eemantojamu Teefu\nturreht/ un eekſch tahs dshwoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nu turrajt/ un dar-\nrarjt wiſſus Likkumus un wiſſas\nTeefas / ko es jums schodeen\npreeftſchleefu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Chee irr tee Likkumi un\ntahs Teefas/ ko jums\nbuhs turreht un darriht\ntai Seimme / ko tas KUNGS\ntawu Tehwu Deews tew dewis\neemantoht wiſſu Mubſchu / ko\njuhs wirs tahs Seimmes dsh-\nwojat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pohſtijeet gluschi wiſſas\ntahs Weetas/ kur tee Pagani /\nko juhs eemantofeet / farweem\nDeetweem irr kalpojſchi/ us ang-\nſteim Kalneem un us teem Pa-\nkalneem / un appalſch falteem\nRohkeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un jums buhs winnu Al-\ntarus apgahſt/ un winnu Stab-\nbuſs falaust/ un winnu elkadee-\nwigns kuplus Meschus ar Uggu-\nni fadeſſinaht/ un winnu Deewu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "isgreeftas Bildes nozirſt / u-\njums buhs winnu Wahrdug n-\ntahs Weetas isdeldeht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jums ne buhs tam KlIN-\nGA M juhsam Deewam ta-\ndarriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet pehz tahs Weetas/ k-\ntas KUNGS juhsu Deews n-\nwiffahm juhfahm Ziltim isre-\ndsehs/ fatvu Wahrdnu tur eeze-\ndams/ pehz winna Mahju-Wee-\ntas buhs jums waizahrt / un u-\nturren buhs tew nahkt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tur buhs jums west juh-\nfus Dedſamus-Uppurus/ un juh-\nfus Uppureus/ un juhsue Defini-\ntus / un juhsas Rohkas Pazel-\nschanns-Uppureus/ un juhsas Ap-\nſohlſchannas / un juhsus Uppu-\nrus/ kas no fabba Brahta / uu-\njuhsn Wehrſchu / un juhsu fihs-\nLohpu Pirindſummufchus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tur buhs jums un juh-\nſeem Nammeem ta KUNG-\njuhsa Deewa Preeſcha ehſt un-\npreezatees/ pahr wiſſu / ko juh-\nfas Rohkas atnefs / ar ko tas\nKUNGS taws Deews tew ir-\nſwehtijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tew ne buhs darriht pehz-\nwiſſu/komehs ſcheit ſchodeen dar-\nram / ikweens ko wiſſch ſchfee-\npareiſi efaim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo juhs ne effat lihds ſchim-\npee Duffſchannas uahkuſchi/ ned-\npee ta Ihpaſchuma/ ko tas Kungs-\ntaws Deews tew dohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet jums irr ja-eet pahr-\nto Jardanu / un jadsihwo tai-\nSemmē/ ko tas KUNGSjuhsu\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
